         14 |C
         15 |C USAGE:  CALL ERRSTOP (IOUTUPRT, ERRMSG2)
         16 |C   INPUT ARGUMENT LIST:
         17 |C     IOUTUPRT - UNIT NUMBER OF THE PRINT FILE.
         18 |C     ERRMSG2  - ERROR MESSAGE OF 2 LINES OF 70 CHARACTERS EACH.
         19 |C                IN THE CALLING ROUTINE, ERRMSG2 CAN BE SET UP
         20 |C                IN THE FOLLOWING MANNER:
         21 |C
         22 |C                CHARACTER*35 ERRMSG(4)
